title: SculptHouse Pop-up Show/ Boutique
text:
12:00 p.m. Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015 Categories 
Events, Sports It’s time to add fashion to your fitness! SculptHouse, a high-quality fitness destination opening in Buckhead this winter, will have a pop up show/ boutique at the Blondes vs. Brunettes Alzheimer’s event on Saturday, October 10. SculptHouse Boutique combines luxury, comfort, and fashion, carrying Athleisure workout clothing from designers such as Koral, Michi, Primsport, Candida Maria, and Zara Terez. Kickoff is at noon at the North Springs High football field.
